data.description: Welcome to this beautiful two-story home with lots of upgrades, new flooring throughout the house, granite counter tops in the kitchen, back splash, new appliances and more. Located in an outstanding location close to major highways (Grand Parkway and I10), shopping, restaurants and zoned to the desirable KATY ISD SCHOOLS!!! This 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath home comes with a spacious backyard, pool and covered patio, perfect for entertaining! A must see…it won’t last long!!!
